CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776769395
OL,3,CWarm days, cold nights: What is behind
OL,4,Cthis week's big temperature gap?
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FComing into spring, the sea and the
OL,12,Fland are cold from winter, and so the
OL,13,Frelative heat from a sunny day is
OL,14,Fquickly lost once the sun goes down.
OL,15,FThis is particularly pronounced if the
OL,16,Fskies are clear and there is no cloud
OL,17,Fto act as an insulator trapping in the
OL,18,Fwarm air.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
